"snippet": "Learning apparatus and method for approximating CNN are disclosed. ... a 
learning method for approximating a CNN (Convolutional Neural Network) ... 
CNN에서는 기본적으로 컨볼루션(convolution) 연산을 통해 영상의 특징을 추출
하기 위한 ... 삼성전자주식회사 시스톨릭 배열을 이용하여 딥 러닝 연산을 수행하는 
방법 및 장치."

column417: "dc.description": "Learning apparatus and method for approximating CNN are disclosed. According to an aspect
column418: a learning method for approximating a CNN (Convolutional Neural Network) including a plurality of convolutional layers includes a step of approximating one of a plurality of convolutional layers using a low rank approximation method Changing the number of output restoration filters of the approximated convolution layer within a range smaller than the number of output restoration filters according to the approximation; and changing the structure of the CNN based on the approximation result and the number of output restoration filter number changes And learning the changed CNN."
